r7635 | jdorje | 2005-11-19 02:38:11 +0100 (Sa, 19 Nov 2005) | 3 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/gtk-games/spades/client_main.c

Parse GTK options before parsing game options; otherwise --g-fatal-warnings
causes the client to exit.

