r4491 | jdorje | 2002-09-09 06:51:32 +0200 (Mo, 09 Sep 2002) | 6 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/chess/board.c
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/chess/board.h
