r1853 | jdorje | 2001-06-26 22:57:01 +0200 (Di, 26 Jun 2001) | 2 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/ggzcards/dlg_main.c
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/ggzcards/hand.c
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/ggzcards/layout.c
