r824 | perdig | 2000-10-21 17:46:36 +0200 (Sa, 21 Okt 2000) | 12 lines
Geänderte Pfade:
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/combat/callbacks.c
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/combat/combat.glade
   M /trunk/ggz/game_clients/combat/game.c
